          <source>To flip the button vertically, set the <ph id="ph1">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Media.ScaleTransform&gt;</ph> object's <ph id="ph2">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Media.ScaleTransform.ScaleY%2A&gt;</ph> property instead of its <ph id="ph3">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Media.ScaleTransform.ScaleX%2A&gt;</ph> property.</source>
